txt_content:
 本帖最后由 孤独秋叶 于 2016-1-9 11:56 编辑 

第一天你需要做的事

原文:
Things to do: 
Cut down at least 1 tree; 
Make a crafting table; 
Make 4 sticks; 
Make a sword, a pickaxe; 
Try to find animals for food and coal; 
Use your leftover time to find resources; 
When it gets dark, find a cave or dig inside a mountain. Dig  at least 11-20 cobblestone and make a furnace, a stone picaxe and a stone sword. Cook your food with your leftover wooden tools. Also cook your iron if you found any. If you can, sleep the night away. (Or use your time on something else) 

CHECKLIST: 
-Trees 
-Food 
-Cobble, coal, iron 
-Other resources 
*Great spots for your house/base, ravines etc. 

!YOU CAN ALWAYS CUT DOWN MORE TREES, DIG MORE COBBLE, DO ANYTHING WHAT ISN'T IN THIS LIST!



翻译:
要做的事：
至少砍1棵树;
做一个工作台;
做4木棍;
做一把剑和一个镐;
试着找找动物，收集食物，煤炭;
用你的剩余时间来寻找资源;
天黑时，发现一个山洞或挖一个洞穴躲到里面。挖至少11-20圆石，做一个熔炉，就可以做石镐和剑石了。你剩余的木头工具拿来烧食物。另外去挖一个铁锭，如果你有床的话，就去睡觉吧。 （或者在剩余时间做点别的事情）
清单：
- 树
-食品
-圆石，煤，铁
- 其他资源
*做你的房子/基地，山洞，反正做的大一点
除此以外你可以在别的时候去砍树，收集资源，做房子，反正这个表是你第一天该做的事~

